Class CcddScriptDataAccessHandlerStatic

java.lang.Object
CCDD.CcddScriptDataAccessHandlerStatic
public class CcddScriptDataAccessHandlerStatic extends Object
CFS Command and Data Dictionary static script data access class. This class contains static public methods that are accessible to the data output scripts
